Title: BAYESIAN STATISTICS 6, pp. 000--000  On the automatic choice of reversible jumps  
Author: J. M. Bernardo, J. O. Berger, A. P. Dawid and A. F. M. Smith (Eds.) PAOLO GIUDICI and GARETH ROBERTS 
Keyword: DIMENSION MATCHING, GRAPHICAL MODELS, JUMP PROPOSAL DISTRIBUTION, REVERSIBLE JUMP MCMC.  
